        "discriminators": [
          "Hand-powered by definition: a rake, hoe or shovel is gritty friction against soil and gravel plus sparse metal clanks. It must NOT contain a sustained motor bed — that would be TOOLPowr or a MACHINES-GARDEN machine.",
